'''ABC Shepparton''' (call sign: '''3GVR''') is an [[ABC Local Radio]] station based in [[Shepparton, Victoria]], broadcasting on the frequency 97.7&nbsp;MHz. It separated from [[ABC Goulburn Murray]] in circa 2006.

